---
title: Roast Pork Belly & Creamy Lemon Mash with Braised Cabbage, Red Wine Jus & Pecans
description: Get ready for a bit of bliss on a fork because it’s roasted pork belly tonight. The zesty lemon stirred through the creamy potato
mash and a serving of nutty broccoli really helps to send your tastebuds to their happy place.
